# Activity Detector

Detects current computer activity based on active window and browser URL.

## Setup
pip install pynput

## Run
python activity.py

## Activities detected
- coding (VS Code, Terminal, Colab, GitHub)
- studying (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, StackOverflow)
- youtube
- wasting (Instagram, Twitter, Netflix)
- browsing (everything else)

## Controls
Press Q to stop
